title: Isekai Tensei Yuri Anthology
description:
Anthology of yuri oneshots by various authors.
Cover: Minakata Sunao
Table of contents:
A Goddess' Blessing and a Convenient Life in Another World by Nonaka Yuu
I am a Princess for Just One Knight by merryhachi
The Case of Being Confined by a Yandere Girl in Another World by Numachi Doromaru
A Harem Skill Was Equipped by Default by Ihara Rio
The You I Met Reflected in Me by Kiyan
The Essence of the You I Met Once Again by Kiyan
A Succubus' Love by Sekihara
Starting Life as a Cat in Another World by Sumire
